        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Reduces cognitive load:</span> Frees brainpower for actual word-finding instead of tile-hunting.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Technique 4 — Chunk Recognition</h2>

    <p>Expert players do not see individual letters — they see chunks. Just as experienced readers process words as units, experienced Scrabble players see tile groups as building blocks.</p>

